channel.title: 718 error
channel.description: EDIT: Ok, I fixed my client crashing problem by updating the cache. It wouldn't load mapdata correctly. But after adding the new cache my client won't even load up, and I get the same error I got when it would crash before. But before it even says "Checking for Updates" in the client it crashes. Any help appreciated. [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/fvcuuu.png[/img]
